{"tid":145470,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"<認真討論>有冇巴絲打教我點欣賞張學友歌聲","createTime":"2017-03-06T09:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T09:09:06.000Z","uid":83913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb493a8565ba757f63cddc3648ed149290af098e","tid":145470,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"我知道張學友唱歌係公認好聽<br />\n<br />\n但我想知其實大家欣賞佢既原因同細節位係點<br />\n<br />\n我自己對音樂認識唔太深，所以品味可能差少少<br />\n<br />\n我會覺得佢既音色好實，好夠氣，一定唔會走音<br />\n<br />\n但會覺得佢好似首首歌都差唔多演譯方法，變化不大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解我會覺得佢有少少油腔滑調<br />\n<br />\n好似下面佢唱陳百強，我覺得佢唱得節奏太有節奏感(唔識點形容，即係好似個首歌好smooth好跳動<br />\n<br />\n會覺得無果種真摯誠懇、感動人既感覺<br />\n<br />\n反而覺得係一個唱歌好勁既人係度show off <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h7IFX6dPrAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh7IFX6dPrAw&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f278f4ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h7IFX6dPrAw</a>"},{"pid":"de517e706a26e918fa949706246c161075434aa9","tid":145470,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d92f943ad699811d6f059a091e973b0673aa9ab","tid":145470,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"李香蘭"},{"pid":"dcaa6dd23ba5abc233b1a6e1411d3e80bb0c4f2c","tid":145470,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"點解張學友唱歌咬字啲尾音要扮鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978e1b5c186bea596453ed10049778d789d09841","tid":145470,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李香蘭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得「是杯酒漸濃」個「是」字有D奇怪"},{"pid":"f227451c78de